		[%
			var
				values = input.values,
				blankImageUrl = '//asset.zcache.de/assets/graphics/s.gif'
			;

			for (var valueNo = -1; ++valueNo &lt; values.length;) {
				var valueDetails = values[valueNo].valueDetails;
		%]
			&lt;div
				id="page_productTypeReviews_sortTop_palette_value-option[%= valueNo %]"
				class="
					ZazzleOptionsSelector-option
					[%= 
						false
							|| !valueDetails.attributes
							|| !valueDetails.attributes['_newgroup']
								? ''
								: 'ZazzleOptionsSelector-newgroup'
					%]
				"
			&gt;
				



&lt;div id="page_productTypeReviews_sortTop_palette_value_option[%= valueNo %]" class="ZazzleSelectorValueDisplay ZazzleSelectorValueDisplay-Horizontal"&gt;
	

	
	&lt;div class=" ZazzleSelectorValueDisplay-highlightDisplayName"&gt;
		&lt;table class="ZazzleSelectorValueDisplay-table"&gt;
		
			&lt;tr class="ZazzleSelectorValueDisplay-tableRow"&gt;
				
				&lt;td id="page_productTypeReviews_sortTop_palette_value_option[%= valueNo %]-displayData" class="ZazzleSelectorValueDisplay-displayData" &gt;
					&lt;label id="page_productTypeReviews_sortTop_palette_value_option[%= valueNo %]-displayName" class="ZazzleSelectorValueDisplay-displayName" for="page_productTypeReviews_sortTop_palette_value_option[%= valueNo %]-input"&gt;[%= valueDetails.name %]&lt;/label&gt;
					
				&lt;/td&gt;
				
			&lt;/tr&gt;
			
		&lt;/table&gt;
	&lt;/div&gt;

	
&lt;/div&gt;
			&lt;/div&gt;
		[%
			}
		%]
		
			
[% /* ]]&gt; */ %]
&lt;/script&gt;

		
		
	&lt;/div&gt;

	
&lt;/div&gt;
	&lt;/div&gt;
	
&lt;/div&gt;
